---
title: fft_field (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_check_inv : check inv flag
    q_check_inv --> q_inv_path : inv == True
    q_check_inv --> q_fwd_path : inv == False
    q_inv_path --> q_compute_invlen : invlen = len(vals).pow(BLS_MODULUS - 2)
    q_compute_invlen --> q_inv_fft : result = _fft_field(vals, reversed roots)
    q_inv_fft --> q_scale : scale each x by invlen
    q_scale --> [*] : return scaled result
    q_fwd_path --> q_fwd_fft : result = _fft_field(vals, roots_of_unity)
    q_fwd_fft --> [*] : return result

    note right of q_check_inv
        INV: When inv=True, applies inverse FFT normalization factor 1/N
        INV: Inverse FFT reverses roots_of_unity order (except first element)
    end note
